lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps edged old foe Ryan Lochte in a pulsating 200 meters individual medley showdown at the U.S. Olympic trials on Friday, adding another thrilling chapter to the greatest rivalry in swimming.

headline.main: Phelps, Lochte Add Thrilling Chapter to Their Rivalry
